sequenceDiagram
    participant I as Instructor
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    I->>B: GET /api/submissions/queue
    B->>DB: Fetch review_pending
    B-->>I: Paginated queue

    I->>B: POST /submissions/:id/claim
    B->>DB: Atomic claim update

    alt Already claimed
        B-->>I: 409 Conflict
    end

    B->>DB: Fetch submission + AI result
    B-->>I: Submission with AI result

    I->>B: PUT /submissions/:id/review
    B->>DB: Set status=completed
    B->>DB: Store human result

    alt Score diff > 0.5
        B->>DB: Set audit flag
    end

    B->>DB: Record skill score
    B->>DB: Update progress
    B-->>I: Final scores
